description: A humorous punchline about a boy who stopped digging holes.
title: Douglas
n_1: Dad and Son are in the backyard, talking.
c1_1: Hey, what do you call a boy who stopped digging holes?
n_2: Dad grins as he gets ready to deliver the punchline.
n_3: They both laugh together at the joke.
n_4: Dad and Son continue their conversation, smiling.
